kb3.name: kb3_factions
kb3.structure: CREATE TABLE `kb3_factions` ( `factionID` int(11) NOT NULL, `factionName` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL, `description` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL, `raceIDs` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `solarSystemID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `corporationID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `sizeFactor` float DEFAULT NULL, `stationCount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `stationSystemCount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `militiaCorporationID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `iconID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`factionID`), KEY `factionName` (`factionName`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
